lli spoke to Sky News after a chaotic press conference where the association's president Umar Kremlev labelled the International Olympic Committee corrupt.\", \"from\": 381, \"to\": 581, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 381, \"end\": 384, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9998521288294628, \"rank\": 0.00014425031511340773, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}, {\"begin\": 439, \"end\": 447, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_News\", \"score\": 0.9998564928363728, \"rank\": 0.00014352772374662658, \"text\": \"Sky News\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_News\"}, {\"begin\": 515, \"end\": 519, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Umar\", \"score\": 0.9999947390615179, \"rank\": 5.260604883551714e-06, \"text\": \"Umar\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Umar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Umar\"}, {\"begin\": 541, \"end\": 572, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr Martelli said the two boxers, Algerian Imane Khelif and Taiwan's Li Lu-Ting, had returned tests in 2022 and 2023 which showed they had male XY chromosomes, prompting their disqualification from the 2023 World Championships in India.\", \"from\": 583, \"to\": 818, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 616, \"end\": 624, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9988312680826984, \"rank\": 0.0006671707898500843, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}, {\"begin\": 625, \"end\": 637, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421623295, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}, {\"begin\": 642, \"end\": 648, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\", \"score\": 0.9980657952826106, \"rank\": 0.0016969291677515956, \"text\": \"Taiwan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\"}, {\"begin\": 651, \"end\": 653, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithium\", \"score\": 0.8438153737917554, \"rank\": 0.1850933640503965, \"text\": \"Li\", \"types\": [\"Q11173\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithium\"}, {\"begin\": 812, \"end\": 817, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.7333681599161032, \"rank\": 0.2762915099772671, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If a boxer is a man, they should not fight at all a woman,\\\" Mr Martelli said.\", \"from\": 820, \"to\": 898, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That's not a statement, it's just normal.\\\"\", \"from\": 900, \"to\": 943, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The International Olympic Committee, which permanently banned the IBA last year due to governance concerns, has disputed the IBA's tests, labelling them arbitrary and ad hoc.\", \"from\": 945, \"to\": 1119, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 949, \"end\": 980, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1011, \"end\": 1014, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9998521288294628, \"rank\": 0.00014425031511340773, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}, {\"begin\": 1070, \"end\": 1073, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9998521288294628, \"rank\": 0.00014425031511340773, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The IOC has allowed the boxers to compete in Paris, due to the fact they have female passports.\", \"from\": 1121, \"to\": 1216, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1125, \"end\": 1128, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.763167201167309e-25, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1166, \"end\": 1171, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999644588730938, \"rank\": 3.554239008729766e-05, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr Mantelli was asked about the IOC's statements that the boxers had been born female and had always identified as women.\", \"from\": 1218, \"to\": 1339, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1221, \"end\": 1229, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adriano_Mantelli\", \"score\": 0.9999999995327471, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mantelli\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adriano_Mantelli\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adriano_Mantelli\"}, {\"begin\": 1250, \"end\": 1253, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.763167201167309e-25, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Regarding this it's not my field and if I answer you I would maybe say something which is not appropriate with the medical language and I would just ruin your answer because I am not a doctor,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1341, \"to\": 1544, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If you ask me if a coach should ever allow a man fighting a woman, then absolutely not, because there is no comparison.\\\"\", \"from\": 1546, \"to\": 1667, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He also hit back at the IOC for questioning the validity of the IBA's tests.\", \"from\": 1669, \"to\": 1745, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1693, \"end\": 1696, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.763167201167309e-25, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1733, \"end\": 1736, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9998521288294628, \"rank\": 0.00014425031511340773, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This exactly goes into the politics matter,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1747, \"to\": 1801, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is a lot of fights between the IBA and IOC and we all know that.\", \"from\": 1803, \"to\": 1874, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1841, \"end\": 1844, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9998521288294628, \"rank\": 0.00014425031511340773, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}, {\"begin\": 1849, \"end\": 1852, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.763167201167309e-25, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If the IBA is so bad why would they disqualify two boxers (after) having two tests, thinking that they are dangerous for the division to take care of the boxers.\", \"from\": 1876, \"to\": 2038, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1884, \"end\": 1887, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9998521288294628, \"rank\": 0.00014425031511340773, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Is this a bad move?\\\"\", \"from\": 2040, \"to\": 2060, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If a federation is taking care of the safety of the boxers because they find out that two tests consecutively are giving the same result so they take a decision which is protecting the boxers.\", \"from\": 2062, \"to\": 2255, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not see anything wrong.\\\"\", \"from\": 2257, \"to\": 2286, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr Mantelli also defended Mr Kremlev, who launched an extraordinary and personal attack on the IOC and its president Thomas Bach, labelling the Paris Opening Ceremony a disgrace and saying the Olympic Committee had destroyed women's sport.\", \"from\": 2288, \"to\": 2527, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2291, \"end\": 2299, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adriano_Mantelli\", \"score\": 0.9999999995327471, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mantelli\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adriano_Mantelli\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adriano_Mantelli\"}, {\"begin\": 2383, \"end\": 2386, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.763167201167309e-25, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 2405, \"end\": 2416, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Thomas Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He felt, probably, quite offended from the Opening Ceremony and this is his reaction,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2529, \"to\": 2625, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2573, \"end\": 2589, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics_opening_ceremony\", \"score\": 0.945118118397018, \"rank\": 0.0416293820062151, \"text\": \"Opening Ceremony\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics_opening_ceremony\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics_opening_ceremony\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Let us put it this way, if this Opening Ceremony truly hurt a lot of people, it's like receiving a big punch in the face, then we are boxing, we give it back.\\\"\", \"from\": 2627, \"to\": 2787, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To join the conversation, pleaselog in.Do not have an account?Register  Join the conversation, you are commenting asLogout  Our Apps\", \"from\": 2789, \"to\": 2921, \"entities\": []}]}"